Emily Kuroda https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Emily_Kuroda 0 Emily Kuroda (born October 30, 1952) is an American actress. She is best known for her role as Mrs. Kim on TV's, Gilmore Girls, but she has had a long career on stage and screen and is a veteran of East West Players, Los Angeles's premier Asian American theater group.
